metadata.description: Featured on Orange County-based producer wes mills’ video game-inspired debut EP ‘nintendo 64,’ “goldeneye 007” pays homage to the iconic game of the same name. Filled with pulsing beats, soaring synths, and dynamic rhythms, “goldeneye 007" takes you on a sonic journey through the game’s most memorable moments. Presenting three more video game-inspired songs such as “nintendo 64” and “grand slam”, the EP celebrates the nostalgia and excitement of the classic gaming console while showcasing wes mills’ signature blend of UK Garage and Dance Pop.

lyrics.text: I got this feeling in my heart
